<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Simple Quiz</title>
</head>
<body>

    <h2>General Knowledge Quiz</h2>

    <form>

        <p>1. What is the capital of India?</p>
        <input type="radio" name="q1"> Mumbai<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q1"> Delhi<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q1"> Chennai<br><br>

        <p>2. Which language is used for web pages?</p>
        <input type="radio" name="q2"> C<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q2"> HTML<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q2"> Python<br><br>

        <p>3. Which is the largest planet?</p>
        <input type="radio" name="q3"> Earth<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q3"> Mars<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q3"> Jupiter<br><br>

        <p>4. Who invented the computer?</p>
        <input type="radio" name="q4"> Charles Babbage<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q4"> Newton<br>
        <input type="radio" name="q4"> Einstein<br><br>

        <input type="submit" value="Submit Quiz">

    </form>

</body>
</html>
